1
00:00:58,053 --> 00:01:01,029
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:01,029 --> 00:01:02,999
=Episode 8=

3
00:01:02,999 --> 00:01:07,021
(Disguise Technique)

4
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:11,168
I thought you had skill, but now,
you defile this painting with blood.

5
00:01:11,584 --> 00:01:14,000
It just seems a performance
to attract attention.

6
00:01:20,879 --> 00:01:24,959
Are these the snow-covered plum blossoms
from your dreams?

7
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:29,959
Seize her.

8
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:30,840
Leave.

9
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:32,680
Master.

10
00:01:33,519 --> 00:01:35,719
I said leave.

11
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,480
(Why did he...?)

12
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:04,400
You know who I am.

13
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:07,560
And you know
the origins of this painting.

14
00:02:08,879 --> 00:02:09,560
Yes.

15
00:02:10,599 --> 00:02:12,280
So you're truly here to kill me.

16
00:02:13,759 --> 00:02:14,319
No.

17
00:02:15,479 --> 00:02:17,520
But I did come with a purpose.

18
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:22,520
At first, I wondered
why you wanted this painting.

19
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:26,159
And among all those painters,
none satisfied you.

20
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:28,280
That's when I realized

21
00:02:28,439 --> 00:02:30,800
what you wanted wasn't a painting.

22
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,520
But later, I changed my mind.

23
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,120
That's not right.

24
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:36,840
Plum blossom painting?

25
00:02:37,039 --> 00:02:38,719
Blinded painters?

26
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:40,960
You were merely venting your rage.

27
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,560
Why do you say that?

28
00:02:43,039 --> 00:02:47,319
What people want most
is always a path to survival.

29
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,639
But what you seek

30
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:52,800
is a path to death.

31
00:02:54,439 --> 00:02:55,439
Continue.

32
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:59,280
Though you appear dandy and glorious,

33
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,919
your face is gaunt and weary.

34
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,879
Your legs can't bear prolonged standing.

35
00:03:06,199 --> 00:03:07,680
All because of this incense?

36
00:03:10,159 --> 00:03:13,840
This incense has narcotic
and muscle-weakening effects.

37
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:18,000
At first, I thought
you set this for the painters.

38
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:23,159
Then I realized someone used it on you.

39
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,199
Long have I heard of
your extraordinary talents.

40
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:31,800
As for your marriage to Princess Shang,

41
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:34,639
she went to the Emperor herself
and asked for it.

42
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,560
But I also heard

43
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:40,759
before wedding Princess Shang,
you had a wife.

44
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,599
Initially, I assumed

45
00:03:43,039 --> 00:03:46,479
you abandoned her for ambition.

46
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:49,080
What puzzles me is

47
00:03:49,759 --> 00:03:54,039
that you almost hoped I was an assassin.

48
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:59,840
So I suspected deeper secrets.

49
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,879
What you want

50
00:04:03,319 --> 00:04:05,039
is never a painting.

51
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:07,319
No.

52
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,080
That's not true.

53
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:14,280
I never abandoned Meiniang.

54
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:22,959
You're from the Xuanji Pavilion.

55
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,160
Don't worry.

56
00:04:30,439 --> 00:04:32,480
I'm not fishing for information.

57
00:04:32,959 --> 00:04:37,319
But I've heard
the Xuanji Pavilion knows all secrets

58
00:04:37,839 --> 00:04:40,720
and sells all intelligence.

59
00:04:41,079 --> 00:04:44,279
Once, I wanted to seek an answer.

60
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,639
I searched everywhere for you people.

61
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:52,160
But unfortunately, I never found any.

62
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:54,839
To climb to this position,

63
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:58,879
I took bribes, bent the law,
and abetted tyrants.

64
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:04,399
My hands are stained
with countless people's blood.

65
00:05:05,959 --> 00:05:07,959
I know I'm no virtuous man.

66
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:11,480
But I've been waiting for your arrival.

67
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,319
She...

68
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,839
She imprisoned Meiniang.

69
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:20,360
I only wanted to find Meiniang

70
00:05:21,399 --> 00:05:22,800
and leave with her.

71
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,040
But

72
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,120
since a few months ago,

73
00:05:32,319 --> 00:05:35,120
all traces of Meiniang have vanished.

74
00:05:35,839 --> 00:05:38,519
I dreamt of our old courtyard.

75
00:05:45,319 --> 00:05:46,720
So much blood.

76
00:05:48,519 --> 00:05:50,519
It stained the snowy ground

77
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:54,480
like the plum blossoms we once admired.

78
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:59,199
Her clothes were soaked crimson,

79
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:06,040
hanging from a plum tree.

80
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,079
She is...?

81
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,199
She...

82
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,720
She

83
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:33,519
is none other
than the lofty Princess Shang.

84
00:06:34,639 --> 00:06:36,759
I sent people to investigate secretly.

85
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,399
But not a single one made it back alive

86
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:42,759
from that small plum garden.

87
00:06:43,279 --> 00:06:47,120
She told me I was overthinking.

88
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,040
But she

89
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,560
addicts me to this incense

90
00:06:55,079 --> 00:06:57,879
to control me.

91
00:07:02,879 --> 00:07:04,920
I can't go search for Meiniang.

92
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,439
Now, I can't even

93
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:09,360
choose death.

94
00:07:10,079 --> 00:07:11,040
Later,

95
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:14,399
I resolved

96
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,600
to drag her down with me

97
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:19,519
even in death.

98
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:23,680
I kept aiding her shady schemes,

99
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:27,040
forming secret factions
and persecuting loyalists.

100
00:07:28,519 --> 00:07:30,720
But I always left evidence.

101
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:36,519
Though sometimes,
she'd find and erase those traces.

102
00:07:36,959 --> 00:07:38,360
But even the most meticulous person

103
00:07:39,279 --> 00:07:40,720
can make mistakes.

104
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:43,839
Then there are the painters.

105
00:07:44,879 --> 00:07:45,920
You are right.

106
00:07:47,839 --> 00:07:49,759
I am waiting for the Xuanji Pavilion.

107
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:55,560
I am waiting for those
who want to bring me down.

108
00:07:56,759 --> 00:07:59,639
I never truly wanted
any plum blossom paintings.

109
00:07:59,879 --> 00:08:02,560
I want the world to see my brutality.

110
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:13,480
I'll make all the Princess's people
join Meiniang in death.

111
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:23,439
It seems you deduced everything,
so you painted plum blossoms with blood,

112
00:08:24,439 --> 00:08:26,040
betting that I'd listen to your words.

113
00:08:27,279 --> 00:08:28,879
So I think you know

114
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,759
what exactly I want to ask.

115
00:08:32,879 --> 00:08:34,200
Is Meiniang truly...?

116
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:37,519
I know nothing about Meiniang's fate.

117
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,279
Then why would you paint with blood?

118
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,279
Because I do know

119
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,600
your old acquaintance

120
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,639
has already passed away.

121
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,480
Go check. Old home, old friend.

122
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:59,240
If there's no time to report back,
a blue signal means all is well.

123
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:03,039
If plum trees exist
at his old home, use orange.

124
00:09:03,799 --> 00:09:06,720
But if more urgent matters
arise, use pink.

125
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:09,000
What do you mean by urgent?

126
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,080
A murder case.

127
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:16,399
Do you truly want
to find the Xuanji Pavilion?

128
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,080
It doesn't matter.

129
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:23,360
Now, I know who this person is.

130
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:34,759
I have a ledger that can topple
Princess Shang and her faction.

131
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,639
I will find a way to give it to you.

132
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,279
Break the door down.

133
00:09:42,048 --> 00:09:43,060
Yes.

134
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:56,840
What? All these guards aren't enough?

135
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:59,240
Must you personally supervise?

136
00:10:00,759 --> 00:10:02,519
I am concerned for your safety.

137
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,240
Where is she?

138
00:10:05,519 --> 00:10:06,360
Who?

139
00:10:07,519 --> 00:10:10,320
Today, I just invited a painter.

140
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:13,799
Once the painting was done,
she naturally left.

141
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:17,879
Search!

142
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:20,879
Capture the assassin
targeting the Consort at all costs.

143
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:21,559
- Yes.
- Yes.

144
00:10:26,879 --> 00:10:33,120
Honey, do you think leaking information
to the Xuanji Pavilion

145
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,679
could overthrow me?

146
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:44,480
Be quick.

147
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:53,639
Aren't you curious about how I know

148
00:10:55,679 --> 00:10:57,440
she works for the Xuanji Pavilion?

149
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:01,759
Fine.

150
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,440
Let me tell you.

151
00:11:07,559 --> 00:11:10,399
The Xuanji Pavilion
now has a new master.

152
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:15,480
Your precious evidence

153
00:11:15,519 --> 00:11:19,919
has become nothing more than
a bargaining chip to win my favor.

154
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,759
No matter what I do,

155
00:11:25,279 --> 00:11:28,799
the royal blood flows through my veins.

156
00:11:29,279 --> 00:11:31,879
People will always
step forward to vouch for me.

157
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,039
Pei Lang.

158
00:11:40,279 --> 00:11:43,600
I can let bygones be bygones

159
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:48,960
as long as you stay
by my side from now on.

160
00:11:49,919 --> 00:11:50,799
Is that okay?

161
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:53,320
"Letting bygones be bygones."

162
00:11:54,279 --> 00:11:57,519
You, a killer, say you'll let it slide?

163
00:11:58,759 --> 00:12:00,000
Killer?

164
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:06,080
Have you believed some wild rumor?

165
00:12:06,639 --> 00:12:07,679
Let me think.

166
00:12:10,399 --> 00:12:12,679
I did coincidentally
send someone to investigate.

167
00:12:13,519 --> 00:12:16,759
Your first wife is indeed dead.

168
00:12:17,919 --> 00:12:19,000
But

169
00:12:22,039 --> 00:12:23,679
she died of illness.

170
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:35,879
Do you think I don't know
where you went on the 15th last month?

171
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:43,360
When you returned,
a plum blossom was on your clothes.

172
00:12:48,159 --> 00:12:49,360
So what?

173
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:55,080
As long as you are my consort,

174
00:12:56,919 --> 00:12:58,320
you remain so for life.

175
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:02,840
We are in the same boat now.

176
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:05,399
If I rise, you share the glory.

177
00:13:05,559 --> 00:13:08,480
If I fall, don't expect
to emerge unscathed.

178
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:11,879
Do you think the Xuanji Pavilion's help
can change anything?

179
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,559
With them?

180
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:16,000
Do they dare?

181
00:13:19,320 --> 00:13:19,960
Wrong.

182
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:24,840
I don't know how you learned a member
of the Xuanji Pavilion was here.

183
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,399
But I know

184
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:31,240
if you truly didn't care,
you wouldn't have come personally.

185
00:13:31,519 --> 00:13:35,039
Nor would you mobilize
your guards for this search.

186
00:13:38,519 --> 00:13:39,960
You are right.

187
00:13:40,519 --> 00:13:42,240
The court situation is chaotic.

188
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:46,279
Those holding your secrets
may not want to overthrow you.

189
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:48,360
But you aren't certain.

190
00:13:49,399 --> 00:13:51,399
You don't know who that person is.

191
00:13:52,279 --> 00:13:53,200
So,

192
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:57,159
you won't risk your wealth and status.

193
00:13:58,559 --> 00:13:59,279
Yes.

194
00:14:00,639 --> 00:14:02,919
I deserve death.

195
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:05,159
But I will

196
00:14:06,679 --> 00:14:11,000
take you with me

197
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:15,799
as an offering for Meiniang.

198
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:23,039
Consort.

199
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:26,080
Rest well.

200
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:41,399
Dianchun, go back swiftly
and search the Consort's room.

201
00:14:41,519 --> 00:14:42,019
No.

202
00:14:42,879 --> 00:14:44,559
Search the whole mansion thoroughly.

203
00:14:45,679 --> 00:14:49,919
Since he has decided to oppose me,
he definitely has a backup plan.

204
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:52,519
If you find any evidence,
report to me immediately.

205
00:14:52,559 --> 00:14:53,159
Yes.

206
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:18,120
I thought you looked familiar just now.

207
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:21,679
So this is the disguise technique
you mentioned.

208
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:23,700
I...

209
00:15:28,639 --> 00:15:29,720
Why are you here?

210
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:31,840
The Princess has given the order.
Split up and search.

211
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:32,600
I'll go over there.

212
00:15:34,919 --> 00:15:36,879
Just go. Don't worry about me.

213
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:44,519
How could I leave you behind?

214
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:26,799
Search.

215
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:28,880
After finding the person,

216
00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:30,559
kill them.

217
00:17:30,559 --> 00:17:31,319
- Yes.
- Yes.

218
00:17:40,611 --> 00:17:42,519
(Princess Royal's Mansion)

219
00:17:42,519 --> 00:17:44,200
Princess Shang has ordered to search.

220
00:17:44,319 --> 00:17:45,000
- Yes.
- Yes.

221
00:17:45,193 --> 00:17:52,000
(Princess Royal's Mansion)

222
00:18:10,279 --> 00:18:11,079
Master.

223
00:18:20,559 --> 00:18:22,160
You're foresighted.

224
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:24,864
I just found this,
and the Princess's people returned.

225
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:27,920
(Ledger)

226
00:18:27,920 --> 00:18:30,960
Princess Shang seems
uninvolved in court affairs.

227
00:18:31,440 --> 00:18:35,119
She rejected the General
and the Right Chancellor,

228
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:37,039
but actually, she's been stirring up

229
00:18:37,079 --> 00:18:39,039
plenty of trouble for her own gain.

230
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:43,200
But with this evidence,
it's enough to bring her down

231
00:18:43,519 --> 00:18:46,200
and clear the innocent subjects' name.

232
00:18:48,240 --> 00:18:51,519
And I left a branch
of plum blossoms in the box.

233
00:18:52,039 --> 00:18:55,160
I wonder what expression
she will have when she sees it.

234
00:18:56,319 --> 00:19:01,599
Princess, I found this hidden
in the Prince Consort's study.

235
00:19:24,079 --> 00:19:26,400
It's a pity I can't see it.

236
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:32,160
Master, I will now take
the ledger to General Shen

237
00:19:32,200 --> 00:19:33,240
and let him tomorrow...

238
00:19:35,319 --> 00:19:36,079
Give it to her.

239
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:38,680
What?

240
00:19:40,559 --> 00:19:42,960
Master, this is absolutely unacceptable.

241
00:19:43,359 --> 00:19:46,480
How can we just hand over
something we worked so hard to get?

242
00:19:47,720 --> 00:19:51,400
Besides, we still don't know
who issued this task.

243
00:19:51,759 --> 00:19:54,480
If the person is not seeking
to topple Princess Shang

244
00:19:54,559 --> 00:19:56,480
but rather to hold
this leverage against her...

245
00:19:57,599 --> 00:20:00,640
It doesn't matter. We live by the blade.

246
00:20:01,359 --> 00:20:03,559
Why dread its edge?

247
00:20:44,272 --> 00:20:49,335
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

248
00:20:49,872 --> 00:20:55,193
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

249
00:20:55,760 --> 00:21:02,388
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

250
00:21:02,388 --> 00:21:07,152
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

251
00:21:07,152 --> 00:21:09,488
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

252
00:21:09,488 --> 00:21:16,188
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

253
00:21:16,188 --> 00:21:22,960
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

254
00:21:22,960 --> 00:21:30,096
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

255
00:21:30,096 --> 00:21:34,480
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

256
00:21:34,480 --> 00:21:37,104
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

257
00:21:37,104 --> 00:21:43,738
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

258
00:21:43,738 --> 00:21:50,288
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

259
00:21:50,288 --> 00:21:57,412
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

260
00:21:57,502 --> 00:22:01,872
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

261
00:22:01,872 --> 00:22:04,580
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

262
00:22:04,580 --> 00:22:10,480
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

263
00:22:11,120 --> 00:22:17,108
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

